---
title: Walnut Pancakes Serves 2 | with Apple Compote and Bacon
description: Ultra fluffy pancakes get a quick pan fry in butter, then get topped with maple syrup and apple compote! Crispy bacon is the only side that matters!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/walnut-pancakes-c541d553-1bcf7db3.jpg
